data.description: Gorgeous fully remodeled walk out basement home in Glendale Schools. Convenient location close to Hwy 65 and Sequiota Park trails. Boasting 4 bed 3 full baths, a media room, & fully open living basement. *New Roof *New HVAC *New Windows *New Siding *New Granite *New Baths *New Tile *Refinished Hardwoods *New Carpet *Updated Electrical * 2 Wood Burning Fireplaces *Patio *Fenced Yard *2 Car Attached Garage  Too many great features to list them all. Come take a look!*Listing Agent is the spouse of managing member for seller, Say You Can LLC.
